            . I lost a carpet on the 9th of August; it stood on a table on the outside of my shop. I saw the prisoner in the act of pulling it away with his apron. I immediately went up stairs, and the prisoner had then got about fifty yards from the shop with the carpet. I pursued him, crying stop thief, and he dropped the carpet.</p>
